data.description: Huge pool home! Discover true Florida Living with this 4 bed, 3 bath, 2 car garage home with Key West Style pool in highly sought after ALL AGES gated community in Magnolia Lakes located in St Lucie West.  This floor plan is perfect for living and entertaining guest providing privacy and tranquility.  Enter through the large front porch and step inside through the double door entryway and admire the elegant porcelain tile flooring.  Volume ceilings with large living areas including formal dining, living and family room and large kitchen.  A grandiose master bedroom overlooking the sparkling pool.  Large walk in closets, over sized master bath with dual vanity, separate shower and tub, Large guest bedrooms with three full baths to make all your visitors feel right at home.
